* Separate the uses of PREFIX and DESTDIR.
http://www.freebsd.org/doc/en/books/porters-handbook/porting-prefix.html

### Move sites out of marla proper

It'd be nice if Marla only contained the code we use to manage websites, rather
than having everything in one repo. I originally liked this arrangement because
it's simple, but it's also going to be quickly cumbersome. Of course, doing this
will be a pretty hefty redesign, but I think it'll be worth it once things
settle down.

